{"article_id":"xaP65wx92QsIZ1SL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Family announces death of channel ' s ousted founder and former presidential adviser , a key force","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"in shaping contemporary media and politics","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"Roger Ailes , the controversial , visionary founder of Fox News","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"who was forced out of the company amid a sexual harassment scandal ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"has died aged 77 .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Ailes , a former presidential adviser , joined the network in 1996 ,","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"building it into the major conservative force in American politics , a profits powerhouse for Rupert Murdoch ' s 21st Century Fox and a company","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"now mired in scandal .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Fox News","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"( @ FoxNews )","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"Breaking News :","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Former Fox News chairman and CEO Roger Ailes has died ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"his family announced .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"pic.twitter.com/AksPdNSZaI","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"\" I am profoundly sad and heartbroken to report","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that my husband , Roger Ailes , passed away this morning , \"","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"said his wife , Elizabeth Ailes , in a statement","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"published on the Drudge Report .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"\" Roger was a loving husband to me , to his son Zachary , and a loyal friend to many .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"He was also a patriot ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"profoundly grateful to live in a country","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"that gave him so much opportunity","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"to work hard ,","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"to rise","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"- and to give back . \"","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"Palm Beach county medical examiner ' s office said","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Ailes died of a subdural hematoma","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"- or bleeding on the brain -","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"caused by an earlier fall in the bathroom of his Florida home .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"The death has been ruled accidental .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Arguably no contemporary figure has shaped media and politics as profoundly as Ailes .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"A successful local TV producer","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"who went on to become a key adviser to a succession of Republican presidents ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"he jumped at the chance","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"to lead Fox News","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"when the service was launched in 1996 .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"In a statement , Murdoch called Ailes a \" brilliant broadcaster \" .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"He said :","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"\" Roger and I shared a big idea","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"which he executed in a way","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"no one else could have .","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"In addition , Roger was a great patriot","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"who never ceased fighting for his beliefs .","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"At 21st Century Fox we will always be enormously grateful for the great business","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"he built .","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"Our thoughts and prayers are with his wife Elizabeth and son Zachary . \"","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"Ailes advised presidents Ronald Reagan and Richard Nixon ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"with whom he once plotted to bring Republican news to television .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"After his exit from Fox last year he was briefly an adviser to Donald Trump ' s election campaign .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"President George HW Bush was among those","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"who paid tribute on twitter .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"George Bush","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"( @ GeorgeHWBush )","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"He was n't perfect ,","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"but Roger Ailes was my friend","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"& I loved him .","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"Not sure I would have been President w/o his great talent , loyal help .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"RIP .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"David Folkenflik , NPR ' s media correspondent and author of Murdoch ' s World : The Last of the Old Media Empires , called Ailes a \" a towering and twisty figure with a very complicated legacy \" .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Ailes ' s \" intentional collision of politics and TV \" redefined broadcast journalism .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"He \" had a willful disregard","depth":15},{"id":61,"text":"of where lines should be drawn , \"","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"and he \" denigrated the work of others in the same field \" ,","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"Folkenflik said .","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"There has been real journalism at Fox News ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"he said ,","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"\" but that was never the point of the network \" . \"","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"Ailes provided the mirror for the distorted image","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"that many conservatives had of how the mainstream media worked .","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"This was enormously successful financially ;","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"it was enormously successful","depth":15},{"id":71,"text":"at morphing Republican party politics .","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"His successes allowed for his excesses .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"... You can not understand this scandal","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"[ that led to his ousting ]","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"without understanding the paranoid and punitive atmosphere","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"he created inside Fox News , \"","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"said Folkenflik .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"His shocking departure from Fox News in July 2016 , after two decades of leadership , signaled the end of an era for the network ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"which has been in turmoil ever since .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Ailes was forced out","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"following allegations","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"that he sexually harassed employees","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"including the former host Gretchen Carlson ,","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"who alleged in a lawsuit","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"that Ailes fired her","depth":16},{"id":86,"text":"after she refused to have sex with him .","depth":16},{"id":87,"text":"She worked at the network for 11 years ,","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"and said","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"during that time ,","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"Ailes subjected her to \" severe and pervasive sexual harassment \" .","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"Ailes reportedly received a $ 40m payout for his departure","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and was to remain as a consultant to the network through 2018 .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"The departure of Ailes was followed later by that of his star presenter Bill O ' Reilly ,","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"also forced out over claims of sexual harassment ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"which he denies .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Douglas Wigdor , a lawyer","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"representing 21 alleged victims of racial and sexual harassment at 21st Century Fox ,","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that Ailes ' passing would not affect the legal process .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"\" In terms of our cases , I don ' t see his sudden passing having any impact","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"as , to the extent relevant , our clients will still be able to testify about his conduct ,","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"which presumably will be more difficult for Fox News to counter","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"given that his testimony was not secured by sworn testimony to date . \"","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"The harassment scandal cast a shadow over Murdoch ' s £11.7bn takeover bid for Sky , the British television network .","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"His attempt","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"to acquire Sky in 2011","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"was thwarted amid the phone hacking scandal .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Wigdor travelled to London last week","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"to meet with the British media regulator , Ofcom ,","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"which is investigating","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"whether Murdoch and 21st Century Fox are \" fit and proper \" owners of Sky .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"Wigdor said","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"that Ofcom could only properly consider the company ' s fitness","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"if Fox waived gagging orders on victims","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"and allowed them to speak to the UK media regulator .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"Though Ailes left Fox in disgrace ,","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"network hosts honored the former chairman on-air through the morning broadcasts .","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"\" Many people out there would say","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"that he saved this country","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"by starting the Fox News channel , \"","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"said the Fox and Friends co-host Ainsley Earhardt ,","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"who cried","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"as she paid tribute to Ailes .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"\" Roger gave every single one of us on this couch an opportunity .","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"He put food on our table ,","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"and you know ,","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"he went out in such a sad way","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"-","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"but who doesn ' t have sins ?","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"We all have our sins ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"we all have our cross to bear ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"and Roger , I will love you forever . \"","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"Shortly after Ailes ' s death was announced ,","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"the Fox News host Bill Hemmer said :","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"\" This is not an easy day . \"","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"Hemmer , with his co-host Shannon Bream , discussed how much Ailes \" loved this country \"","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"and recalled how Ailes would invite Fox News employees to his house in the Hudson Valley .","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"\" And we would stand","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"and salute the flag ,","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"and that is how the evenings began at Roger ' s house , \"","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"he said .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":283,"left":143,"right":282,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":143,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":148,"right":281,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":145,"right":147,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":144,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":144,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":5,"right":146,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":169,"right":280,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":149,"right":168,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":152,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":151,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":10,"right":150,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":162,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":155,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":153,"right":154,"relatio